      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780053034190,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2) How can we ensure that the system is fault tolerant and durable?\n    ✅ Use mesaage queue\n            - Durable Storage\n            - Buffering Against Load Spikes\n            - Ordering Within an Auction (Partitioning by auctionId)",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2) How can we ensure that the system is fault tolerant and durable?\n    ✅ Use mesaage queue\n            - Durable Storage\n            - Buffering Against Load Spikes\n            - Ordering Within an Auction (Partitioning by auctionId)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HS9E5LQa7R-RVGNx8RW-j",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 26005.450404767795,
      "y": 2015.9618263512327,
      "width": 1057.643310546875,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#228be6",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1856468525,
      "version": 333,
      "versionNonce": 1081083363,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780053034190,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3) How can we ensure that the system displays the current highest bid in real-time?\n    ❌ Websocket - overkill here    \n    ✅ Long polling for max bid\n    ✅ ✅ SSE",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3) How can we ensure that the system displays the current highest bid in real-time?\n    ❌ Websocket - overkill here    \n    ✅ Long polling for max bid\n    ✅ ✅ SSE",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
